Speedemissions Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















speedemissions inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Waste & Environ Svcs & Equip
Sub-Industry: Pollution Control Equipment
Speedemissions Inc. opens, acquires, develops, and operates vehicle emissions testing stations.  The Company currently operates several facilities in Georgia and Texas under the Speedemissions trade name.




