			Company Description 


			Speedemissions, Inc. engages in the business of conducting vehicle emission and safety inspection tests automobiles, vans, sport-utility-vehicles, and pick-up trucks. It owns and operates vehicle emission and safety inspection testing stations in Georgia, Missouri, and Utah. The company was founded ...
		


                Speedemissions, Inc. engages in the business of conducting vehicle emission and safety inspection tests automobiles, vans, sport-utility-vehicles, and pick-up trucks. It owns and operates vehicle emission and safety inspection testing stations in Georgia, Missouri, and Utah. The company was founded in March 2001 and is headquartered in Tyrone, GA.
            




